data.description: Nestled in the serene Lakeside subdivision of Laredo, Texas, this captivating 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence exudes elegance and comfort. Step into a haven of tranquility, where modern living seamlessly blends with a touch of traditional charm.    As you enter, your eyes are drawn to the impressive wood staircase with iron railing, gracefully ascending to the bedrooms upstairs. The well-appointed kitchen, adorned with a sleek middle island and a bar for casual dining, beckons you to gather with loved ones for delectable meals and cherished moments.    Retreat to the upper level, where four bedrooms await, each offering a sanctuary of relaxation and rejuvenation. The master suite, a true oasis of tranquility, pampers you with a luxurious en suite bathroom, ensuring a spa-like experience every day.    Step out onto the expansive backyard, enclosed by a private stucco fence and gate, and discover an idyllic retreat for outdoor activities. Host unforgettable gatherings, let children frolic freely, or simply bask in the tranquility of your private sanctuary.    Close to schools, grocery stores, shopping, restaurants and much more.    This exceptional home, nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, is the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Embrace the serenity of Lakeside living and create memories that will last a lifetime.    Don't miss this rare opportunity to own this exquisite piece of Laredo real estate.
